                      PSUEDO CODE

void setup()
    initialise I2C communication
    get the 0 offset for gyroscope and accel readings.
    Initialize the pin change interrupts and set it to the bluetooth channels

void loop()
    update the IMU readings
    Convert it to degrees/sec
    Feed these readings into PID control loop
    get the PID output 
    call the OTHER SUBROUTINES accordingly.
    Complementary filter to reduce the noise.
    Update the 4 channel inputs
    Using these updates and

OTHER SUBROUTINES FOR quad movements

SUBROUTINES for PCI interrupts

Subroutine for pid calculation, roll/pitch/yaw update
